<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #222;
    }
    .container {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 10px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px;
    }
    th {
      background: #eee;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Low Internal Marks Alert</h2>
    <p>Dear {{name}} (Reg No: {{regNo}}),</p>

    <p>We have observed that your internal assessment marks in the following subject(s) are below expectations:</p>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Subject</th>
          <th>Marks</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{{subjectMarks}}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>We advise you to consult with your respective subject faculty and take corrective actions to improve your performance.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      Sincerely,<br />
      Class Advisor<br />
      {{institutionName}}
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
